    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You inhale and take a charging stance, manifesting ripples of lightning release chakra throughout your entire body. You coat your knee in a sharp coat of lightning and rapidly strike and an creature with it, hitting them directly in the stomach.</p><p>Make a melee taijutsu attack, dealing your unarmed damage + 3d4 Lightning damage, this jutsu ignores half of a creatures damage reduction.</p><p><strong>Overcharge:</strong> When you cast this jutsu, as a bonus action or reaction, you can overcharge its effects. When you do this the affected creature must make a constitution save gaining a rank of slowed on a fail.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above <br />D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the damage by 2d4, if this jutsu is cast at B-Rank or higher you ignore damage reduction entirely.</p>",
